#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/gpio_control.rst:2
msgid "GPIO Control"
msgstr "GPIO控制"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/gpio_control.rst:4
msgid ""
"Your OpenMV Cam has between 9 (OpenMV Cam M4) to 10 (OpenMV Cam M7) "
"general purpose I/O pins onboard for talking to the real-world. We're "
"probably going to keep the pin count this low moving into the future to "
"keep the OpenMV Cam tiny."
msgstr ""
"您的OpenMV Cam板上有9个（OpenMV Cam M4）到10个（OpenMV Cam M7）通用I/"
"O引脚，用于与现实世界通信。未来，我们可能会保持引脚数较低，以保持OpenMV "
"Cam的小巧。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/gpio_control.rst:8
msgid "Anyway, there are a few ways to use GPIO pins."
msgstr "无论如何，有几种使用GPIO引脚的方法。"

